author: Just Jared
title: Dakota Johnson Can't Stop Laughing During 'Mad Lib Theater' with Jimmy Fallon (Video)
text:
Dakota Johnson made an appearance on The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon on Tuesday night (January 31) and participated in a hilarious, Fifty Shades Darker -themed version of Mad Lib Theater!
The 27-year-old actress had to say random words to fill in the blanks for a scene that she would then perform alongside Jimmy .
The scene was a reenactment of Anastasia Steele and Christian Grey’s first meeting in his office in the movie Fifty Shades of Grey .
Dakota couldn’t stop laughing from the hilarious things she had to say and it was such a funny segment!

Mad Lib Theater with Dakota Johnson (Fifty Shades Darker Edition)
